{"type": "article", "id": 24669, "title": "放手机或平板的支架", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-30T07:00:59Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110423XVs9UDZuTB4xciwL.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是一个专门放手机或平板的支架，试图让你的双手不再一直握着它，从而保持放松的姿势。设计原理和夹在桌边的台灯是一样的，它的固定方式是用螺丝旋转的，更稳定。这套支架的头还配有 5、7、10 英尺这 3 种型号的夹子以方便放多个工具。售价 48 美元，<a href=\"https://fancy.com/things/991699611141800827/Gooseneck-Lazy-Mount\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110420lLDBuvi6zGt4EPyg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.91125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110420YMFOKsn5aRtoVbDf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110421GkmKqpYHxwfsFea6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.91625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110421dSy0OXFDEluITQYH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110422O8Y6PoET7ZlSctHK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.485\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702110422gUYnGBmSudk3eisX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}